  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/3ca3c9d7764535eeebaa0672dcc05331.poster.avif?t=1748877225\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/3ca3c9d7764535eeebaa0672dcc05331.webm?t=1748877225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/3ca3c9d7764535eeebaa0672dcc05331.mp4?t=1748877225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Case of Distrust is a narrative mystery from 1924 San Francisco. Play as private investigator Phyllis Cadence Malone in this historical 2D adventure game. Explore underground speakeasies, smoke-filled billiard halls, classic barber shops, and more. Catch suspects in lies by using evidence, statements, and your wits. Intrinsic challenges face our heroine, as she struggles against a pushback on emancipation, leading to many doubts, both internal and external. Uncover the truth in a mystery full of deception!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Critical Reception</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Perfect video game noir... 9/10\" - Polygon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Impressed me with its nuanced, careful construction\" - Newsweek</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Stunning two-dimensional silhouettes\" - PC Gamer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Beautiful noirish graphics... suspenseful mystery\" - Vogue Magazine</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/1cb289b9ffe2999959de5302696da2a4.poster.avif?t=1748877225\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/1cb289b9ffe2999959de5302696da2a4.webm?t=1748877225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/1cb289b9ffe2999959de5302696da2a4.mp4?t=1748877225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hardboiled mystery, working past deceptive characters towards the truth</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1924 San Francisco with historically accurate details</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saul Bass inspired visuals and scene transitions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finger-snapping music that gives style to the roaring 20s</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Themes of poverty, racism, and emancipation that tie into contemporary issues</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/3ca3c9d7764535eeebaa0672dcc05331.poster.avif?t=1748877225\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/3ca3c9d7764535eeebaa0672dcc05331.webm?t=1748877225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/3ca3c9d7764535eeebaa0672dcc05331.mp4?t=1748877225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Case of Distrust is a narrative mystery from 1924 San Francisco. Play as private investigator Phyllis Cadence Malone in this historical 2D adventure game. Explore underground speakeasies, smoke-filled billiard halls, classic barber shops, and more. Catch suspects in lies by using evidence, statements, and your wits. Intrinsic challenges face our heroine, as she struggles against a pushback on emancipation, leading to many doubts, both internal and external. Uncover the truth in a mystery full of deception!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Critical Reception</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Perfect video game noir... 9/10\" - Polygon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Impressed me with its nuanced, careful construction\" - Newsweek</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Stunning two-dimensional silhouettes\" - PC Gamer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Beautiful noirish graphics... suspenseful mystery\" - Vogue Magazine</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/1cb289b9ffe2999959de5302696da2a4.poster.avif?t=1748877225\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/1cb289b9ffe2999959de5302696da2a4.webm?t=1748877225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717610/extras/1cb289b9ffe2999959de5302696da2a4.mp4?t=1748877225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hardboiled mystery, working past deceptive characters towards the truth</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1924 San Francisco with historically accurate details</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saul Bass inspired visuals and scene transitions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finger-snapping music that gives style to the roaring 20s</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Themes of poverty, racism, and emancipation that tie into contemporary issues</p></li></ul>",
